        <li>2nd highest seed winner vs. highest seed winner</li>
        <li>See Playoff Brackets for the remaining loser's bracket and/or Toilet Bowl games.</li>
      </ul>
      <strong>Week 17 Championship Week</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Semi Final winners will play for the League Championship.</li>
        <li>Semi Final losers will play for 3rd and 4th place.</li>
      </ul>
